# Cross-agent skills (Claude, Cursor, Codex)

When working on Tessera, follow the **central agent skills** so Cursor, Claude, and Codex all contribute without overwriting each other.

- **Read** `docs/AGENT_SKILLS.md` for the full reference.
- **Principle:** Extend and improve; avoid replacing or contradicting committed behavior unless the user explicitly asks.
- **Cursor focus:** Implementation in this repo (APIs, CLI, tests, protocol layer). Respect specs in `docs/` and existing swarm/transfer/token behavior.
- Before large refactors or reimplementations, prefer small additive changes or documenting the proposal; let the user decide.
